找單字














 
    crossover    
      

IPA [ˈkrɔsˌovɚ, ˈkrɑs-]
KK [ˋkrɔs͵ovɚ]



 定義
 影片字幕 (193)
 俚語 




解釋n.[生]（雜色體的）雜交，交換；[鐵路]岔道，轉線路；（交搭胸前的）女圍巾；天橋；
例句This amplifier and crossover network drive the subwoofer mentioned above.該放大器和交叉的網路驅動器上面提到的低音炮。Need to design crossover operator rationally while optimizing ANN.優化網路需要合理設計交叉運算元。To prove the seriousness of his crossover bid, he brought several American stars on stage.為了證明他的文化交流的嚴肅主題，他也邀請了幾位美國明星。The Taiwan singer gave a crossover performance of traditional folk music and Western pop.台灣歌手王力宏創作了民族和流行跨界的音樂。Nearly all serious loudspeaker designs have incorporated a crossover network.幾乎所有嚴肅的揚聲器設計都會涉及分頻網路。 




探討美國越戰的失敗原因The Vietnam War: Reasons for Failure - Why the U.S. Lost




01:45:58






         that we reach what's called we called the crossover ports a general william       

我們呼籲，我們達到什麼叫做  交叉端口一般威廉      



         the crossover point needs       

需求的交叉點      






